  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Story</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >'The Fall' is a story of three foreign students at a private British boarding school. Becoming information brokers within the school walls brought them money and respect, but knowledge can also bring trouble. The forbidden fruit was forced in their mouths and its taste will remain forever. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3140330/extras/a4d71f4583039c316a40165fe87afe44.poster.avif?t=1742482814\" width=600 height=254 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3140330/extras/a4d71f4583039c316a40165fe87afe44.webm?t=1742482814\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3140330/extras/a4d71f4583039c316a40165fe87afe44.mp4?t=1742482814\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Confrontation of cultures, the difference in upbringing and in relation to punishments - these form the integral part of 'The Fall’ and the foundation of a difficult, ambiguous, forked and sometimes comical story of three friends, who found themselves in an unknown world, in which, according to all the canons of such stories, nothing is what it seems to be.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >3 very unstable main characters.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dark academia aesthetic.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Angry Abu.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >40000+ words.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >4 endings. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Joke about a goat (a very good joke).</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Many beautiful locations.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3140330/extras/0e16963a4ae531cd2e92c98590757295.poster.avif?t=1742482814\" width=600 height=254 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3140330/extras/0e16963a4ae531cd2e92c98590757295.webm?t=1742482814\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3140330/extras/0e16963a4ae531cd2e92c98590757295.mp4?t=1742482814\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
